{"code":200,"message":"","data":{"id":"10018","movieId":"18","title":"巨富与我们","tag":"BBC","desc":"一个有关超级土豪的纪录片。","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/eich-and-us.jpg","introduces":[{"type":1000,"text":"一个有关超级土豪的纪录片。","image":""},{"type":1001,"text":"","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/eich-and-us01.jpg"},{"type":1000,"text":"记者Jacques Peretti走访各种土豪人士、经济学家、平民百姓，研究超级土豪是如何改变了英国。","image":""},{"type":1000,"text":"这部纪录片揭露出所谓的“下渗式经济”是如果令贫富变得更加悬殊的。","image":""},{"type":1000,"text":"英国政府为了政绩把本国打造成富人避税天堂，但30多年来所谓的富人涓滴效应并未惠及底层人民，反而随着金融衍生品和次贷危机使贫富差距加剧而形成沙漏社会。","image":""},{"type":1000,"text":"中产的消亡将进一步削弱资本主义制度。英国如此，世界亦然。","image":""}],"videos":[{"id":"2314","title":"1、第一集","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/eich-and-us.jpg","playCount":"3","playNumber":1,"playNumberDesc":"第一集","playWebUrl":"http://player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid\u003d1931988\u0026cid\u003d2989838\u0026page\u003d1","videoUrl":""},{"id":"2315","title":"2、第二集","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/eich-and-us.jpg","playCount":"3","playNumber":2,"playNumberDesc":"第二集","playWebUrl":"http://player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid\u003d1931988\u0026cid\u003d3029801\u0026page\u003d2","videoUrl":""},{"id":"2316","title":"3、第三集","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/eich-and-us.jpg","playCount":"3","playNumber":3,"playNumberDesc":"第三集","playWebUrl":"http://player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid\u003d1931988\u0026cid\u003d2989839\u0026page\u003d3","videoUrl":""}]}}